name: Pink Supermoon over Winthrop Beach with Pan Motion
description:
The pink supermoon of April 2021 seen rising over Winthrop Beach in Winthrop, Massachusetts before sunset. The image is comprised of a freeze frame at 800mm to capture the moon, and a fast panned ocean at 100mm during Golden Hour. The goal was to get the moon rising over Graves Light, but the line up didn’t work out.

50.3 mpx, 8688 x 5792 px (30 x 20” @ 290 ppi)
